text.tspan: I was playing for a local club, FC Edebei, and
the owner came to my house to tell my parents
of an opportunity in Italy. At first, they were
skeptical in that I was only fifteen; I was
too young. I told them they should let
me go, let’s see what happens
When the opportunity in Milan presented
itself. I was still only sixteen years old. They
told me Ronaldo was on Milan and I asked if
it was the same Ronaldo I’d watch on TV in
Nigeria. I thought I was going to sign and be
placed in the line-up with all these stars!
I was wrong, but was happy to make my way
